  <brief_title>Furcation Treatment With L-PRF and aPDT</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluation of Leukocyte Platelet Rich Fibrin With Antimicrobial Photodynamic Therapy in Treatment of Furcation Involvement: Randomised Clinical Study</official_title>
